      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like you don't get it. it's not even about being \"sad\" really. it's more like... if a tree falls in the woods and nobody's around, it doesn't matter, right? like, if i just drifted away and stopped being part of the loop, it wouldn't be a tragedy. it would just be quiet. it seems almost more peaceful than trying to force myself to feel like a person again. don't you think there's a certain kind of peace in just not being perceived?",
